<caption id="C7906673FFB3FFF245BC4472FCAEFBC0" ID-DOI="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4006318" ID-Zenodo-Dep="4006318" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/4006318/files/figure.png" pageId="3" pageNumber="1602" startId="3.[144,211,1067,1089]" targetBox="[145,1103,169,1034]" targetPageId="3">
<paragraph id="935036FBFFB3FFF245BC4472FCAEFBC0" blockId="3.[144,1104,1067,1118]" pageId="3" pageNumber="1602">
Figure 2. 
<taxonomicName id="54EF4D78FFB3FFF245DB4472FE22FBDE" baseAuthorityName="Wood" baseAuthorityYear="1909" box="[247,443,1067,1088]" class="Insecta" family="Phoridae" genus="Megaselia" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Diptera" pageId="3" pageNumber="1602" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="crassipes">
<emphasis id="A19BEAE9FFB3FFF245DB4472FE22FBDE" box="[247,443,1067,1088]" italics="true" pageId="3" pageNumber="1602">Megaselia crassipes</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
male (synonym of 
<taxonomicName id="54EF4D78FFB3FFF247534475FC88FBDE" authorityName="Disney and Durska" authorityYear="2011" box="[639,785,1067,1089]" class="Insecta" family="Phoridae" genus="Megaselia" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Diptera" pageId="3" pageNumber="1602" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="basiturgida">
<emphasis id="A19BEAE9FFB3FFF247534475FC88FBDE" box="[639,785,1067,1089]" italics="true" pageId="3" pageNumber="1602">M. basiturgida</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
). (A) Left face of hypopygium; (B) posterior face of front tibia and basitarsus. Scale bar: 0.1 mm.
</paragraph>
